the turks and their libyan allies withdrew to the countryside instead of surrendering , and the italians bombarded the cities for three days , then proclaimed the tripolitanians to be " committed and strongly bound to italy . "   this marked the beginning   of a series of battles between the italian colonial forces and the libyan armed opposition in the east of libya ( cyrenaica ) under omar mukhtar for 22 years .

